Incident Response Report: Web Application DoS Attack
1. Introduction

On April 23, 2026, our web infrastructure experienced a significant service degradation. Investigation revealed a Layer 7 Denial of Service (DoS) attack. The attack aimed to overwhelm the server's request-handling capacity, resulting in intermittent "504 Gateway Timeout" errors for legitimate users. This report details the nature of the attack and the proposed mitigation strategies.
